divs: Sighting DetailsI was watching vultures circling when I noticed a faint star-like object, white in color. Sighted nearly due east. I suspected a UFO since it was not moving, and no stars are observable at mid-day. Surprise at the time of the sighting. Had to leave my home. I am a veteran Navy aircrewman with several thousand hours flight time, and amatuer astromer. I notice when I see things in the sky that do not normally belong there.
